sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Controller
    participant N as Node
    participant A as Agent

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over C,N: Phase 1 — SSH deploy (ONE-SHOT)
        C->>N: open SSH
        C->>N: scp agent binary
        C->>N: write config file (auth-token)
        C->>N: systemd enable --now
        C->>N: close SSH
    end

    rect rgb(232, 255, 232)
        Note over C,A: Phase 2 — WebSocket (LONG-LIVED)
        N->>A: agent starts, reads config
        A->>C: open WSS (Authorization: Bearer auth-token)
        A->>C: Register
        C-->>A: Register ack
        loop every 10s
            A->>C: Heartbeat
        end
        A->>C: EventPush (docker events)
        A->>C: LogChunk
        C->>A: CommandRequest (declarative)
        A-->>C: CommandResponse
        C->>A: TokenRefresh (periodic)
        A-->>C: TokenRefreshAck
        C->>A: Shutdown (node teardown)
        Note over A: agent shuts down the node
    end
